        "Description": "The spa is hot and warm, what could possibly go wrong? Well our intel suggests that there are imposters in the area, they might not look threatening but they&apos;re the most dangerous secret agents.\r\rPlanning to overthrow Hokkaido and hack the entire network and AI that could prove to be a catastrophe. You must deal with them in a professional matter to resolve this issue.\r\rGood luck!",
